&lt;p&gt;简单的分析以下，指输入的值只要异或2就行，写个脚本&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;a = &amp;#39;LQQAVDyWRZ]3q]zmpf]uc{]vm]glap{rv]dnce&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;b = &amp;#39;&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;for i in range(38):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; b+=chr(ord(a[i])^2)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;print(b) 
